    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65B40 V8. This unit maintains excellent throttle response through its eight independent throttle bodies and features a robust 6-speed manual gearbox. The rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014critical failure points on this platform\u2014have been proactively addressed, ensuring the internal integrity of the powertrain. The chassis retains its composure with a well-maintained multi-link rear setup and the M Variable Differential Lock providing optimal lateral traction. With double-VANOS timing operating within factory parameters and a rigid subframe, this example represents a technically proficient driver's car that balances visceral performance with a well-documented maintenance history.",
