    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior presents beautifully with a deep luster to the paint; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper from highway commuting, the body remains straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, the cabin has been kept in smoke-free, pristine condition. The leather seats show only light softening from use, and all interior electronics\u2014including the navigation system and heated seats\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is sound. It has a complete service log showing regular oil changes every 5,000 miles and recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, comfortable ride. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for the road today.",
